0:
”Alexa open my indicators”
”Alexa, ask my indicators what is the dollar value”
”Alexa, ask my indicators what is the euro value”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my indicators
des:
If you are Chilean and want to know what are the current values of the principal indicators (dollar, euro, utm or uf), just ask it to My Indicators.
In the first release, we support only one question to get the indicator value, but next releases will be better :D
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
